{"tid":2422842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兒子人有三急船灣淡水湖邊小便 港媽大讚「痾得好」！","createTime":"2021-02-25T13:19:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T05:05:38.000Z","uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"11ebf2378e79aaaf7bd05b0c6d515b8d345029d7","tid":2422842,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T13:19:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f3dd64ef2c8564b064a2b9447e157a77807a6ad","tid":2422842,"uid":63113,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T13:19:40.000Z","msg":"人有三急雖然難忍，但仍應保持公德心，不可隨處便溺。日前有市民在網上表示，在大美篤目擊一名港媽教兒子在船灣淡水湖湖邊小便，更大讚兒子「痾得好」，缺德行為引來網民抨擊。根據資料顯示，船灣淡水湖屬水務署轄下水塘，任何人在集水區污染食水水源恐屬違法。<br />\n<br />\n有網民投稿至facebook專頁「生仔要考牌系列」並上載相片，指近日在船灣淡水湖目擊一名男童在湖邊小便。從照片所見，該名男童面向淡水湖，脫下褲子疑在小解，旁邊一名女士則蹲下扶著男童。目擊者表示，事後男童母親更大讚兒子「痾得好」，<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2886237/%E8%87%AA%E7%A7%81%E7%BC%BA%E5%BE%B7%E2%94%82%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E4%BA%BA%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%89%E6%80%A5%E8%88%B9%E7%81%A3%E6%B7%A1%E6%B0%B4%E6%B9%96%E9%82%8A%E5%B0%8F%E4%BE%BF%E3%80%80%E6%B8%AF%E5%AA%BD%E5%A4%A7%E8%AE%9A%E3%80%8C%E7%97%BE%E5%BE%97%E5%A5%BD%E3%80%8D%E8%A2%AB%E8%BD%9F%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E6%B0%B4%E5%A1%98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2886237%2F%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%25A7%2581%25E7%25BC%25BA%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E2%2594%2582%25E5%2585%2592%25E5%25AD%2590%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%2580%25A5%25E8%2588%25B9%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%25B7%25A1%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%25B9%2596%25E9%2582%258A%25E5%25B0%258F%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25AE%259A%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%2597%25BE%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E3%2580%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25BD%259F%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E6%259F%2593%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%25A1%2598&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFYL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=94e39c82\" target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.